============================================
Game Description:                          =
============================================

The Old City: Leviathan is an experiment in first person exploration
that focuses entirely on story. Everything else is secondary.All that
exists is you and the world. Set in a decaying city from a
civilization long past, The Old City: Leviathan puts the player in the
shoes of a sewer dwelling isolationist. You progress through the
narrative by simply exploring the world

